title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 14 2022

description:
Author and columnist Ann Coulter covers all things leftist lunacy with Clay and Buck. Musk speaks: Talks Twitter during TED talk. Alex Berenson returns to discuss the latest covid data, the Elon Musk Twitter takeover and Twitter's importance. More dumb stuff from Joy Behar of The View.
